<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Action Needed for Your Account</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
            font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.3px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.75;
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <h1>Action Needed for Your Account</h1>

        <p>Hi {{fullname}},</p>

        <p>
            We noticed that we need a bit more information to complete your account
            setup with <strong>{{merchantName}}</strong>.
        </p>

        <p>
            When you have a moment, please open the app to review your account and
            provide the required details.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you,</p>

        <div class="footer">&copy; {{year}}. All rights reserved.</div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>